## [0.1.0] - 2025-09-03
### Added
- Initial release of **Kisan Mitra - AI Farming Assistant**.
- Multilingual support (Hindi, English, Telugu).
- Weather forecasts, crop price info, fertilizer advice.
- Voice input support.
